{"tid":1575971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣辦事疑遭縱火　何君堯斥破壞者「曱甴」　籲 921 清潔十八區牆壁","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T06:33:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99d5051dcfe0a850772d5cd8cda6547b42909812","tid":1575971,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/julius-01_BPedE_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjulius-01_BPedE_1200x0.png&h=613d22d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何君堯facebook專頁<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯位於荃灣荃豐中心二樓的議員辦事處，早前疑遭人縱火。何君堯昨晚在 Facebook 回應事件，屢稱破壞者為「曱甴」，又指警方至今仍未緝拿疑犯，給人辦事不力的感覺。此外，他呼籲市民參加9.21 的「清潔香港運動」，清淨十八區的牆壁。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚，何君堯荃灣辦事處第二次遭人破壞。他遂在Facebook 發帖，指其辦事處被「三隻曱甴」破壞，他們投擲疑似信號彈、雞蛋，並指摘他們「目無皇法」，更稱「誓將那些無膽匪類蒙面曱甴的面罩撕破」。此外，他又認為其辦事處兩個月內連續遭破壞，但警方至今未能緝拿疑兇歸案，令人感覺警方「辦事效率不足」。<br />\n<br />\n其後，他再次於直播片段中提及事件，屢稱破壞者為「曱甴」、「無恥」，並相信「天網恢恢疏而不漏」，犯法的人會受到法律制裁。<br />\n<br />\n此外，何君堯又提到要在10.1 國慶前搞好「清潔運動」，呼籲各區市民參加。全港各區連儂牆遍地開花，但早前何君堯發起9月21日「清潔香港運動」，邀請18區市民「把影響市容的垃圾撕掉，洗淨牆壁，同時人心也要洗，匡正校內校外學習環境」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA-%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E7%B1%B2-921-%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E5%8D%80%E7%89%86%E5%A3%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E7%25B1%25B2-921-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%2589%2586%25E5%25A3%2581%2F&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=9ee569a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E7%25B1%25B2-921-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%2589%2586%25E5%25A3%2581%2F&h=099a214f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA-%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E7%B1%B2-921-%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E5%8D%80%E7%89%86%E5%A3%81/</a>"},{"pid":"b7abaf7f554f911c8251a3c4c6674c29770f2274","tid":1575971,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bde0c59cb61bc51d5f6385185cd2923075e6484","tid":1575971,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:56:22.000Z","msg":"各位藍絲同志到時衣著要統一 一齊著愛國愛港Tee"},{"pid":"4eb3110db1f6c04de53f1b73118111c28ceae8a5","tid":1575971,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/3dDjLhP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dDjLhP.png&h=22cfb35f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}